cinder/volume/driver.py.message:
I would suggest to move this as method in some common utility module as 'get_base_image_ref(volume) and call this method at line #916 as;

base_image_ref=get_base_image_ref(volume)

def get_base_image_ref(volume):
    # if volume is created from image, we pass the base image id to glance
    base_image_ref = None
    if volume.glance_metadata:
        base_image_ref = getattr(volume, 'glance_metadata')['image_id']
    return base_image_ref


This way we can avoid duplication of code in all the drivers.

